# API Layer and Errors

- Never call `axios` directly inside React components.
- All API calls must go through service layer files (`xxx.service.ts`).
- API response types are required; avoid untyped responses.
- Use Zod to validate API responses at boundaries (service layer).
- Do not swallow errors; always handle and surface feedback to users.

```ts
try {
  await dispatch(loginThunk());
} catch (e) {
  toast.error("Login failed");
}
```

- Re-throw or map errors where needed so upper layers can react properly.
